planeswalker left to go get milk or something, but he accidentally brought some of that infecting oil
the spider guardian tried to clean it up and got infected
the spider guardian was able to stop the progression of the disease, but the cure drove him mad
he went crazy, blocking any incoming travelers from entering the world
so when planewalker guy came back with milk he couldn't get back in
however, the spider guardian was also crazy and didn't realize he did this, and was obsessed with leaving the world and finding his maker (whom he locked out)
planeswalkers possess a spark they are born with that allows them to travel between worlds
memnarch built a machine, he couldn't leave, but he could suck others into his empty world
the machine would just teleport a random person from somewhere in the multiverse to him, wiping their memory in the process

all the people who didn't have a spark (all of them) just got dumped outside

most people didn't know about memnarch's existence, but when he learned about the planeswalker he sent his armies after her to capture her and steal her spark
she had a whole hero's journey at the end and killed him

but it would make them more metallic, making them easier to infect for other forms of oil
spider guardian was usually too busy combating the more dangerous outbreaks of oil to worry about mycosynth, and over time many inhabitants of the world had metal aspects in their body
